---
import Box from "./Box.astro";
---


<Box title="What is latest.cat?" class="mb-10 bg-green">
  <p class="mb-4 font-bold">
    Ever struggled to find the latest version of a programming language?
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    <strong class="font-bold">latest.cat</strong> is a simple, fast and free
    way to browse the latest releases of your favorite programming language.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Type your favorite programming language name in the search bar, hit enter
    and you will immediately see the latest releases of that programming
    language.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    You can even use <strong class="font-bold">latest.cat</strong> from the
    command line!
  </p>
</Box>